*  Predefined Functional Interfaces in Java

| Interface       | Method      | Purpose                         |
|----------------|-------------|---------------------------------|
| Runnable       | run()       | Thread execution                |
| Callable       | call()      | Returns result                  |
| Comparator     | compare()   | Sorting                         |
| Predicate<T>   | test()      | Condition checking              |
| Function<T,R>  | apply()     | Takes input and returns output  |
| Consumer<T>    | accept()    | Consumes value                  |
| Supplier<T>    | get()       | Supplies value                  |
